values: Hey guys! So its been a while--ive been so busy gettin ready for AU. First I had to give up my title at the pageant then I had to drive straight here after to start rush. Ive been rushin since last Mon--almost a wk and Im just gettin a chance to let ya no how its goin. Its so tiring and emotionally draining. But today is BID DAY and I find out which sorority Im in so wish me luck. I have a good feeling Ill get my first choice--AOpi! Allison is goin through it with me and it helps havin her here to talk to--we r gonna have so much fun this yr! Ill let ya no how it goes probably tom. Luv yall and I miss u LaLa! : ) Cant wait to see u today.

Hey yall! so i definitely got my fair share of "booty" this summer--haha. One was REALLY HOTT and sweet and we hit it off. and guess what guys...hes actually taller than me! heck yes! we dated for a little bit but it didn't work out since im leavin for AU. but u never no what could happen in the future.

i mean look at this guy!....

Hey yall! So i was thinkin today about how soon we r all leavin. Its crazy! Im really ready to leave and start my own life w/out parents and stuff but at the same time, im leavin everything ive ever known. Its scary :( Im gonna miss my friends the most. I can always come back and see my fam but all my friends are goin aroung the country. Laurens goin to Cali, Brits goin to Ohio, and so many other people are leavin. Dont get me wrong, I want them to leave so I can go visit them. I wanna go to Cali so bad and I really wanna see snow cause the last time I did was the "blizzard of '93" haha! Well anyways, Im gonna miss everyone and I cant wait till Thanksgiving when we can all hang out again. 

Luv yall

I hope AU is ready for me cause Im comin and Im ready to kick some ass in football this yr. :)

O.k. So the Kenny Chesney tickets didnt work out...crap! I really wanted to see him. But its kool cause i still got to spend the whole night w/ Josh. And I really wanna see him again soon. Like today! Brittany..shut up, dont say anything. haha! I guess we r dating. haha! Brit, I hope u r havin fun on ur trip but im glad ur comin home today. I missed u and i gotta update u on everything. So I dont have much to say right now but ill get on again later. Somethin will happen by then. lol! 

Luv yall

Peace out :)

Also Brit, we gotta decide on a Six Flags day-im dyin here. And hopefully Deja Vou(i guess thats how u spell it) is workin this time.

So today im tryin to get tickets to the Kenny Chesney concert. yeah i know its the day of but i have connections at the radio stations. im tryin to set up my table for Natalee tonight too. im tryin to collect about $5000 by the end of the summer-thats my goal. and if i do that maybe they will save some tickets for me. if i only get 2 im takin Josh. he said he really wants to go so i thought it would be cool if i could get tickets and take him. ill let u know what happens and if i do go, ill take pics to put on here.

Here are some pics from last years concert if this tells u how close i got-i went with LeLe and we had to work our way to the front of the stage but we made it-it was like a mosh pit! Rascal Flatts was there too and we got to meet them. its a long story how it happened but it was so cool. i even got to meet Kenny backstage which was really exciting but just look at these pics:

WOW! Its been a while. So much has happened since the last time i wrote on here. First, Brit came back from Switzerland. She got me a really pretty bracelet-im goin to wear it all the time. Then, one night last week, me and her went over to this guy's house named Josh. See i met him at church about a month ago and i thought he was really HOTT! But i didn't know what to say to him so i just kinda said hey every week. Then i decided one night to ask him if he wanted to hang out with our group after church wed night, but he already had plans. I told him we could just do it next week and he got my number and said he'd call sometime. So anyways, me and Brit went over to his house a few nights later and he had 2 friends over. Brit and Calvin really hit it off and of course i still was interested in Josh. Josh left for GA for 4th of July and me, Brit, Calvin, and my sis, Lauren went to see War of the Worlds-which was really wierd and intense but good. Ill just say this, Calvin really liked Brit! So me and Josh have been texted for about a week while hes been in GA and I think we might start dating. We are goin to go see a movie when he gets back. So things are goin good. And ive been helpin the Holloway fam too by collecting money and sending it to her trust fund. I think ive done pretty good. Anyways, im ready for Josh and Brit-yeah she went out of town again-to get back so we can hang out again.

Today has been so funny. We spent all last night doing crazy stuff. We just goofed around-watched movies, got on the computer, ate ALOT! It was fun :) We were really bored though. So anyways, we spent 4 hrs. cleaning Mrs. Hiedi and Mr. John's office and now were goin to get in the pool probably and then were goin over to Kyle's house for some more fun. We tried to teach Brit how to play "MOW" but she got really mad. She sucks basically! O.k., im gonna go now, buh-bye.

So...this is my first entry! Well, Im just hangin with Brit tonight-that's one of best friends from school.  My old school that is-high school. Im on my way to Auburn now! Im so ready because Im tired of my parents looking over me all the time. I like knowin they're there but I wish I could just do what I wanted w/out them knowing everything. I can't wait to get to AU and I can have a little fun...parties, football games (WAR EAGLE!), and hundreds of HOTTT frat guys to choose from. Itll be great! So Im goin to watch a movie right now-Ill talk to ya again tom .
